Output â†’ /home/salman/projects/security

ðŸ“ File Management Commands
| Command        | Description             | Example                         |
| -------------- | ----------------------- | ------------------------------- |
| `touch`        | Create a new empty file | `touch report.txt`              |
| `mkdir`        | Create a new folder     | `mkdir logs`                    |
| `cp`           | Copy a file or folder   | `cp report.txt logs/`           |
| `mv`           | Move or rename a file   | `mv old.txt new.txt`            |
| `rm`           | Remove a file           | `rm temp.txt`                   |
| `rmdir`        | Remove empty folder     | `rmdir logs`                    |
| `cat`          | Display file contents   | `cat report.txt`                |
| `nano` or `vi` | Edit file content       | `nano script.sh`                |
| `find`         | Search for files        | `find /home -name "report.txt"` |

ðŸ“˜ Scenario:
